            "heading": "",
            "sub_heading": "",
            "box_description": "",
            "main_description": "<p>Nestled into the side of the Taradale hills and surrounded by farmland and vineyard, yet only 10 minutes from the city and airport, Mission is a convenient and picturesque winery setting for your wedding.</p>\n<p>The Mission Restaurant has a reputation for outstanding food and we have an experienced and professional team dedicated to providing exceptional service and the extra touches that will make your day extraordinary.</p>\n<p>From the garden ceremony, to picture perfect vineyard wedding photos, right through to the last dance you can place your special day into our hands with confidence.</p>\n<p>Please feel free to call our Functions Manager directly to discuss your wedding plans or to arrange a visit to view our facilities.</p>\n<p><strong>Functions Manager</strong></p>\n<div class=\"wraps_icons_text_tabs\">\n<p><span><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M8 3C8.5 3 10.5 7.5 10.5 8C10.5 9 9 10 8.5 11C8 12 9 13 10 14C10.39 14.39 12 16 13 15.5C14 15 15 13.5 16 13.5C16.5 13.5 21 15.5 21 16C21 18 19.5 19.5 18 20C16.5 20.5 15.5 20.5 13.5 20C11.5 19.5 10 19 7.5 16.5C5 14 4.5 12.5 4 10.5C3.5 8.5 3.5 7.5 4 6C4.5 4.5 6 3 8 3Z\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path>\n</svg> </span> Call: 64 6 844 6003</p>\n<p><span><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M22 6C22 4.9 21.1 4 20 4H4C2.9 4 2 4.9 2 6V18C2 19.1 2.9 20 4 20H20C21.1 20 22 19.1 22 18V6ZM20 6L12 11L4 6H20ZM20 18H4V8L12 13L20 8V18Z\" fill=\"white\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>  Email</p>\n</div>",
